Picker是一组排斥的控件
<!-- more -->
## 声明
```swift
struct Picker<Label, SelectionValue, Content> where Label : View, SelectionValue : Hashable, Content : View
```

### 用法
```swift
class UserInfoes: ObservableObject {
    enum DayInfoes: String, CaseIterable {
        case day1 = "一天一次"
        case day2 = "一天两次"
        case day3 = "一天三次"
        case day4 = "两天一次"
    }
    
    //设置默认选择项
    @Published var dayInfoes = DayInfoes.day1
}

struct ContentView: View {
    @ObservedObject var frequencies = DayInfoes()
    VStack {
        Picker(selection: $frequencies.dayInfoes, label: Text("频率").bold()) {
            ForEach(UserInfoes.DayInfoes.allCases, id: \.self) { season in
                Text(season.rawValue).tag(season)
            }
        }.pickerStyle(DefaultPickerStyle())
    }
}
```

### 设置项

#### .pickerStyle （样式）
1. DefaultPickerStyle（默认）
2. SegmentedPickerStyle（IOS）
3. WheelPickerStyle（IOS）
4. PopUpButtonPickerStyle
5. RadioGroupPickerStyle
